This is a useful document for preparing yourself for ICE in your city. It covers safety and next steps for both immigrants and current citizens.
<a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1gfmgnScnSkyLHANHrgDssTxtsGMQqxyK8nyIeZZEXS4/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Winter Prep Info Sheet</a>

Useful Organizations/Contacts:
The Remix Way: Nashville based immigrant rights collective
  Instagram: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/theremix_way/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@theremix_way</a>
Music City Migra Watch: Middle TN based ICE watchers who alert locals to the presence of ICE.
  Instagram: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/musiccitymigrawatch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@musiccitymigrawatch</a>
Tennessee Immigrant and Refugee Rights Coalition (TIRRC): Nashville based Immigrant and Refugee Rights Organization
  Instagram: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/tnimmigrant/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@tnimmigrant</a>
  Linktree: <a href="linktr.ee/TIRRC" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TIRRC</a>
